snippet.title: SERAPH: In the Darkness Boss Fight Trailer
snippet.description:
🤫 Whispers abound about the Bishop's daughter in SERAPH Alpha Test. 
Some say she holds the keyto unlocking unimaginable power. Others fear her as the harbinger of darkness.🌑
